### [MODIFY] [client_simulator.go](file:///c:/Users/SARIGASINI/OneDrive/Desktop/문서/GitHub/hospital_federated_learning/client_simulator.go)

- Added [Timestamp](file:///c:/Users/SARIGASINI/OneDrive/Desktop/%EB%AC%B8%EC%84%9C/GitHub/hospital_federated_learning/server/security.go#42-64), [Signature](file:///c:/Users/SARIGASINI/OneDrive/Desktop/%EB%AC%B8%EC%84%9C/GitHub/hospital_federated_learning/server/security.go#19-41), and [signPacket()](file:///c:/Users/SARIGASINI/OneDrive/Desktop/%EB%AC%B8%EC%84%9C/GitHub/hospital_federated_learning/client_simulator.go#36-43) function
- Each packet is signed before submission

