## Security Pipeline

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["Receive JSON Packet"] --> B{"verifySignature()"}
    B -- "❌ Mismatch" --> R1["403 Forbidden"]
    B -- "✅ Valid" --> C{"validateTimestamp()"}
    C -- "❌ Stale (>30s)" --> R2["408 Request Timeout"]
    C -- "✅ Fresh" --> D{"Field Validation"}
    D -- "❌ Invalid" --> R3["400 Bad Request"]
    D -- "✅ Valid" --> E{"RoundManager\n(round + duplicate check)"}
    E -- "❌ Rejected" --> R4["409 Conflict"]
    E -- "✅ Accepted" --> F["Store Update"]
    F --> G{"Quorum Met?"}
    G -- "Yes" --> H["Trigger Aggregation"]
    G -- "No" --> I["200 OK — Waiting"]
```

